    "name": "Ankr Liquid Staking API",
    "description": "The Ankr Liquid Staking RESTful API surfaces staking metrics, the trustless\nexchange ratio, and validator metadata across Ankr's liquid staking tokens\n(ankrETH, ankrBNB, ankrPOL, ankrAVAX, ankrFTM, ankrDOT, etc.). It complements\nthe on-chain Smart Contract API exposed on Avalanche, Binance Smart Chain,\nEthereum, Fantom, and Polygon.\n\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Ankr\n Email: support@ankr.com",
